<collectingCountry box="[771,918,1947,1973]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
and the Arabian Peninsula. It is a most unexpected find. It was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[541,689,1983,2009]" name="Mozambique" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Mozambique</collectingCountry>
and further recorded from southern 
<collectingCountry box="[1096,1180,1983,2009]" name="Nigeria" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Nigeria</collectingCountry>
(
